4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the trike##1
6. the teacher is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Hobby       | woodworking | baking    | photography |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| Flower         | amaryllis  | zinnia     | iris        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

