3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
5. the russian is between the person who's hobby is reading and the british##2
6. the fan of salsa is the british##1
7. the russian is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | reading      | sudoku     | collecting |
| Nationality           | dutch | russian | british     |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | rock       | salsa      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

