The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the bike##2
2. the russian is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Nationality      | indonesian    | japanese        | russian |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | sports  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile   | ship    |

