2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
3. the person who's sport is badminton is between the owner of the fish and the argentine##2
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
7. the argentine is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality        | argentine       | brazilian     | canadian   |
| Pet         | dog          | lizard    | fish       |
| Sport       | snowboarding | badminton | ice-hockey |
| Transport   | bus          | van       | skateboard |

